OL,3,CAntakya earthquake: A city of rubble
OL,4,Cand grief remains one year on
OL,6,FOn February 6, 2023, an earthquake
OL,7,Ftore through Antakya, killing 55,000
OL,8,Fand leaving more than a million people
OL,9,Fhomeless
OL,11,FIn the graveyard outside every one of
OL,12,Fthe thousands of headstones bears the
OL,13,Fsame date.
OL,15,FFebruary 6, 2023 is etched in the
OL,16,Fmarble as firmly as in the national
OL,17,Fpsyche.
