OL,3,CAntakya earthquake: A city of rubble
OL,4,Cand grief remains one year on
OL,6,FThere are few events that inflict harm
OL,7,Fon people at the very same moment,
OL,8,Feven war wreaks its hell at different
OL,9,Ftimes.
OL,11,FHowever, 4.17am on February 6 is a
OL,12,Fmoment of shared, enduring trauma.
OL,14,FIn the space of 80 seconds the 7.8
OL,15,Fmagnitude earthquake destroyed lives
OL,16,Fand cities.
OL,18,FA year on the devastation it wrought
OL,19,Fcontinues. In total, 55,000 people
OL,20,Fdied. 1.5 million were left homeless.
