OL,3,CAntakya earthquake: A city of rubble
OL,4,Cand grief remains one year on
OL,6,FIn the past months the bulldozers have
OL,7,Fknocked down street after street. Such
OL,8,Fwas the damage, repair was impossible.
OL,10,FThere is a mixed view of the
OL,11,Fgovernment response, often dependent
OL,12,Fon political loyalty, however few fail
OL,13,Fto appreciate the scale of the
OL,14,Fchallenge.
OL,16,FAntakya, which stood through
OL,17,Fmillennia, is gone. It will be rebuilt
OL,18,Fon the same land but without the soul
OL,19,Fand souls which made it one of
OL,20,FTurkey's most beloved cities.
